abstract: The spending comes as Republican leaders have questioned or denied the established science of human-caused climate change.
snippet: The spending comes as Republican leaders have questioned or denied the established science of human-caused climate change.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — A self-described conservative North Carolina businessman has promised to spend at least $5 million through his political action committee to back five Republican congressional candidates who have supported taking action to curb climate change.

abstract: This artist’s works were among the most radical feminist statements in Europe of the ‘60s and ‘70s.
snippet: This artist’s works were among the most radical feminist statements in Europe of the ‘60s and ‘70s.
lead_paragraph: In 1967, the Austrian artist Waltraud Hollinger jettisoned her family name and the last name her husband had given her and became Valie Export, a nom de guerre inspired by a popular brand of cigarettes. But late last week, at a hotel in the West Village where she was supposed to be staying, the front desk could find no record of a Valie Export having checked in.

abstract: The film adaptation of Ron Suskind’s book about his autistic son includes the animation that helped them communicate.
snippet: The film adaptation of Ron Suskind’s book about his autistic son includes the animation that helped them communicate.
lead_paragraph: When the documentary director Roger Ross Williams read early galleys of his journalist friend Ron Suskind’s book “Life, Animated,” a 2014 memoir about his autistic son Owen’s breakthrough thanks to his identification with Disney’s animated characters, he knew he wanted to tell the story on film and would have to use animation to do so.

abstract: The supercar is the rear-drive version of the all-wheel-drive LP 610-4, but there is more fun in the corners with the 580.
snippet: The supercar is the rear-drive version of the all-wheel-drive LP 610-4, but there is more fun in the corners with the 580.
lead_paragraph: LEGEND has it that in the early 1960s, Ferruccio Lamborghini, an Italian tractor maker, thought the Ferrari sports car he owned could be improved. But his suggestions to the car’s designer, Enzo Ferrari, were rebuffed. Thus began a rivalry, as Mr. Lamborghini entered the performance-car business, resulting in some stunning art and engineering.

abstract: Senator Tom Udall, Democrat of New Mexico, has been praised for holding together an ideologically divided group of senators and steering the legislation to the president’s desk.
snippet: Senator Tom Udall, Democrat of New Mexico, has been praised for holding together an ideologically divided group of senators and steering the legislation to the president’s desk.
lead_paragraph: Congress is getting beat up for its failure to find agreement on gun control in the aftermath of the mass shooting in Orlando, Fla. But on Wednesday, lawmakers will be able to celebrate a rare bipartisan achievement on another issue.

abstract: Mazda has updated the CX-9 with aggressive styling and a turbocharged 4-cylinder engine with more torque than the 6-cylinder it replaced.
snippet: Mazda has updated the CX-9 with aggressive styling and a turbocharged 4-cylinder engine with more torque than the 6-cylinder it replaced.
lead_paragraph: IT’S said that parenthood is its own reward. But giving up the visceral thrill of a sports car for a family vehicle can seem like a penalty.
headline_main: Mazda’s CX-9: A Crossover That’s a Treat for Parents
headline_print_headline: A Three-Row Crossover  That’s a Treat for Parents

headline_main: Orlando, Donald Trump, Hillary Clinton: Your Wednesday Briefing

abstract: The modern equivalent of debtors’ prisons lock people up if they cannot pay.
snippet: The modern equivalent of debtors’ prisons lock people up if they cannot pay.
lead_paragraph: TULSA, Okla. — IN the 1830s, the civilized world began to close debtors’ prisons, recognizing them as barbaric and also silly: The one way to ensure that citizens cannot repay debts is to lock them up.
